{"tid":2381102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：市民前往政府大樓或辦事處　需使用「安心出行」","createTime":"2021-01-26T10:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T11:10:23.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1601c54cdce7d3809e79999f9e178e730df35fa7","tid":2381102,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"政府宣布周四（28 日）起恢復部分基本公共服務，並要求市民前往政府大樓或辦事處時，需使用「安心出行」流動應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n政府由去年 12 月起實施政府僱員特別上班安排，政府發言人今日表示，考慮到社會和經濟運作需要，將會在周四（28 日）恢復部分基本公共服務。有關部門將會自行公布有關安排和會恢復提供的服務的詳情。政府的最終目標是在條件許可下，全面恢復正常公共服務。<br />\n<br />\n但政府亦另設要求，市民在進入重開的政府大樓或辦事處時，遵從相關部門實施的防疫措施，包括使用「安心出行」流動應用程式、體溫檢測和人流控制安排，同時要一直佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人指，希望市民理解，為了減少人流和社交接觸，各政策局和部門會採取彈性措施，盡量減少辦公地點同一時間員工的數目。因此辦事處的開放時間可能會有所更改，市民輪候服務的時間亦可能會延長。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93%E6%88%96%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95-%E9%9C%80%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25BE%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2599%2595-%25E9%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSvxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=13362e66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25BE%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2599%2595-%25E9%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%2F&h=5ccecb72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93%E6%88%96%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95-%E9%9C%80%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C/</a><br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始早前曾指，政府正研究現時被勒令關閉的處所，包括健身中心、美容院、派對房間、夜總會、卡拉 OK 場所、按摩院等重開後，要求營運者檢查光顧客人有無安裝「安心出行」應用程式。"},{"pid":"a4d0c1a83697e3145e2f39d595a1eff75ea393f3","tid":2381102,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"唔用犯法？快d出緊急法<br />\n唔犯法就彩你都有味啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79bb3739675927e2706b9d4ebe8fda8d8d421e9","tid":2381102,"uid":376895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"小弟智障唔識用咪棟喺個門口度塞住出入口等保安慢慢教囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378cad5eaa4668ec349bb4ce1b50b24f370d431c","tid":2381102,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0fb7f03fdccf6ccfa095745b2a982c9d2fcbf2","tid":2381102,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e79bb3739675927e2706b9d4ebe8fda8d8d421e9","tid":2381102,"uid":376895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"小弟智障唔識用咪棟喺個門口度塞住出入口等保安慢慢教囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"服侍廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25aa1ff8218bf9abca09acc34e2410feb00477a1","tid":2381102,"ui